        　　<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"In the next stage, we should further deepen the reform, optimize the business environment, further stimulate the vitality of market players, and strive for better economic performance in the second half of the year." Mao Shengyong said.</p><br/>
            <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The contribution rate of the new economy has increased significantly</p><br>
